[32m"Masked text for sample 1, segment 893-1384: .\n\nLet me try again.\n\nLet's solve the problem step by step. \n\n1. First, calculate the total number of seats in the auditorium.\n2. Determine the number of seats occupied by the administrators.\n3. Calculate the remaining seats after the administrators have taken their seats.\n4. Determine the number of seats occupied by the parents.\n5. Calculate the remaining seats after the parents have taken their seats.\n6. The remaining seats will be occupied by the students.\n\nLet's start by calculating the total number of seats in the auditorium. There are 4 rows with 18 seats each, so the total number of seats is \\(4 \\times 18 = 72\\).\n\nNext, one-fourth of the seats were occupied by the administrators, so the number of seats occupied by the administrators is \\(\\frac{1}{4} \\times 72 = 18\\).\n\nThe remaining seats after the administrators have taken their seats is \\(72 - 18 = 54\\).\n\nOne-third of the remaining seats were occupied by the parents, so the number of seats occupied by the parents is \\(\\frac{1}{3} \\times 54 = 18\\).\n\nThe remaining seats after the parents have taken their seats is \\(54 - 18 = 36\\).\n\nThe remaining seats, which are 36, were occupied by the students. So the number of students is 36.\n\nLet's confirm this with Python code.\n```python\n# Total number of seats in the auditorium\ntotal_seats = 4 * 18\n\n# Number of seats occupied by the administrators\nadministrators_seats = total_seats // 4\n\n# Remaining seats after the administrators have taken their seats\nremaining_seats_after_administrators = total_seats - administrators_seats\n\n# Number of seats occupied by the parents\nparents_seats = remaining_seats_after_administrators // 3\n\n# Remaining seats after the parents have taken their seats\nremaining_seats_after_parents = remaining_seats_after_administrators - parents_seats\n\n# Number of students\nstudents_seats = remaining_seats_after_parents\n\nprint(students_seats)\n```\n```output\n36\n```\nThe number of students in the school auditorium is \\(\\boxed{36}\\).\n\nWait, let me recheck my solution.\n\n"[0m
